	<C> <Lion>

	monitor.c

	Programm for Debug Monitor

Input:
				UART1 - 115200 8n1
				UART2 - 115200 8n1
Oupput:
				Display 128x160

	2019 01 11	v1.0 


This is Debug Module.

Use STM32F103c8t6 Microcontroller board
Use ST7735 spi Display 128x160

You can input 2 serial UART to your Project.
Write what you need to be debug to Serial1 or Serial 2.
See result on Display.

Use HAL Library.
Special thanks https://github.com/afiskon for 7735 Library.
